column5: Way to go   You don't work at Cintas by any chance ? Got my hair cut today and was yackin with the woman who cuts my hair and she know someone who works at Cinta in Newmarket that won the same thing ! Was that you ?  TB
Congratulations Joey. It's nice to know somebody actually wins those. Only a couple coffees for me so far. I keep hoping for the boat. Everytime I roll up the rim I say,"Come to Papa".
Couldn't be happier for you Joey.   :thumbsup_anim:

Joey here,  Nope, not me TB.  Thanks everyone, I'm still beaming.  Although the fiasco that goes with claiming your prize is a whole different matter.  But I'm not going to let that get in the way of my happiness at winning.  Joey
Hey Joey. Great going!! Good to see you win it.
WTG Joey! Nice to see someone win a good prize. BTW, I have all the charts and stuff so if you need anything uploaded.......
WTG Joey congrats  rob
WTG Joey, nice stuff happens to nice people
Very nice win!!  I won my first coffee today   Congrats to you.

Good for you joey congrats girl !!!!!!    hey im on coffee #34 and havnt even won a dam dohnut !!!!!!if it wasnt for bad luck i wouldnt have any at all !!..LOL..LOL.. glad to see someone like you win a great prize
Congrats Joey.
thats awesome Joey!   ( that should mean Paul gets a new fishing rod to balence off the toys)
You are one lucky lady.  I was thinking you could kiss "the thing I fish with" for good luck; but was afraid I'd ruin a good thing with Muskiestudd!
Congradulations Joey. Good things come to good people
Thats great! Congrats!
Wow Joey good for you.  Really though I think all women should have em  Ok Men too cause were too stuborn to ask for directions.  Let us know how well it works
Rolled up my rim this morning and won me a Garmin GPS, Wooooohoooooo!!!!!!   _0312094148_001.pdf   Joey
WOOOOOOOOOOOHOOOOOOOOOOOO! Paul no longer needs to stop for directions!
Might come in handy in Simcoe Blizzard....
Ohh cool, the roll up is back? haven't been to a Tim's in a while.. Congrats Joey!
thats pretty cool. The most i ever won was a free muffin or a cup of coffee.
I'll trade you a free coffee and a free doughnut for the GPS! LOL Congrats... now Paul will know where YOU"RE catchin the fish! HH
WOO HOO!!!  Awesome Joey!  Congrats!
I hope they're giving away more than one, because that's what I wanted.  Congrats
They're giving away 5,000, and 242 have been won to date according to the website, well, 243 now  Joey
Sah-WEEET!  I've just been winning free coffees( 5 so far ), but you just won yourself one of the GOOD prizes!  You'll get some use outta that, for sure.
Congratulations!  Now you can locate every Tim Horton's in Canada!
There's so many Timmies you don't have to actually mark them. Now your favourite fishing locations - that's a different story! Congrats
Does it come with the Fishing HOT spots all Marked  Congradulations
Nice to hear someone is winning the bigger prizes!  I have not won a dang thing on those cups....ever!!! not a donut or a coffee LOL....  Maybe I'm due?
congrats
That's great, congrats. We've won many coffee's, donuts, but that's it. My wife likes to play 3 times a day. LOL
Way to go hon, good on ya.
Congratulations Joey. I finally know someone who has won something!!
Congrats Joey!
You got da luck o' da irish!!  Good for you!!
congrats on the win only coffee and donuts so far for me
Sweet!
Way to go  , Mine always say LOOSER!!!  Thank goodness I don't buy them that often.
Whhhoooo HOOOOOO WTG JOEY....
